'''賈斯汀·威爾森'''（{{lang-en|Justin Wilson}}，{{bd|1978年|7月31日|2015年|8月24日}}），[[英國|英國]]藉職業[[開輪式賽車|開輪式賽車]]選手，曾經參與[[一級方程式賽車|一級方程式]]、[[24小時戴通納|24小時戴通納]]、[[電動方程式|電動方程式]]等賽事，是迄今身材最高的一級方程式車手<ref>{{cite web|last=Glendenning|first=Mark|url=http://www.racer.com/indycar/item/120678-justin-wilson-1978-2015|title=OBITUARY: Justin Wilson 1978 - 2015|publisher=''[[Racer_(magazine)|Racer]]''|date=24 August 2015|accessdate=24 August 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150827174223/http://www.racer.com/indycar/item/120678-justin-wilson-1978-2015|archive-date=2015-08-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2015年8月23日，賈斯汀出賽[[印第賽車系列賽|印第賽車系列賽]]期間，在{{link-en|波科諾賽道|Pocono Raceway}}遇到意外，被前車的碎片擊中頭盔，受到[[創傷性腦損傷|創傷性腦損傷]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://m.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120477 |title=Wilson remains in critical condition - AUTOSPORT<!-- Bot generated title --> |access-date=2015-08-30 |archive-date=2016-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160224223253/http://m.autosport.com/news/report.php/id/120477 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，延至翌日離世，享年37歲<ref name="abcnews">{{cite news|title=IndyCar Driver Justin Wilson Has Died of a Head Injury|date=24 August 2015|publisher=ABC News|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/indycar-driver-justin-wilson-died-head-injury-33293479|accessdate=24 August 2015|archive-date=2015-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150825045249/http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/wireStory/indycar-driver-justin-wilson-died-head-injury-33293479|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

